	<h2><TMPL_VAR NAME="PAGE_TITLE"> Tips</h2>

        <p>Please view the coverage information for search criteria applicable for the state in which you wish to search. A list of available records by state is shown for the Department of Correction, Court Records and arrest logs.</p>
        <p>&nbsp;</p>
        <p>Find a criminal record using one or more of the following search techniques:</p>

	<ol id="font81">
		<li>Search by Name. You can also use a partial first name.<br /><br /></li>
		<li>Search by Name and DOB. This returns records for the listed name with the specified date of birth. <br /><br /></li>
		<li>Search by DOC number, if known.<br /><br /></li>
		<li>Search by Name, State and County. This will return Court Records or Arrest Log information for the listed name within the County and State requested. (Check coverage area for available counties)<br /><br /></li>
		<li>Search by Address, City and State. This will return records containing the requested address.<br /><br /></li>
	  </ol>
	<p>Results vary from state to state but may return the following information: Name, Address, County, Date of Birth, Place of Birth, SSN, DOC Number, Offense State, and Source.</p>
	<p>&nbsp;</p>
	<p>You can purchase a Criminal Report which may contain information from the following sources: Department of Corrections, Court Records, Arrest Logs and Sexual Offender Records.</p>
	<p>&nbsp;</p>


